2. Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    1. Java 6
    2. QuakeLive account.

3. Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    1. Edit configuration.properties.
    2. Scorebot needs QuakeLive account to log in and operate on it. It may be
       your account (but you and bot cannot be both logged in the same time) or
       special account registered for bot.
    3. Use console to start application. For Windows users: Start->Run->'cmd',
       then run start.bat. For Linux users use any shell and run ./start.sh.
       This may be improved in future versions.

4. Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Bot connects to IRC to channels you provide. Use !help for help.
    Availible commands and examples:
        !start ql 726152 - starts scorebot on game id 726152
        !stop K3         - stops scorebot with K3 identifier
        !teams K3 LLL vG - renames teams
        !show K3         - show K3's game status.
        !stop K3         - stops K3.

